snippet.title: Hermano Game Boy is now on Kickstarter!
snippet.description:
Rescue your brother from the depths of hell! HERMANO is our new game for the original GAME BOY console.
Enter our Kickstarter and get your copy now. Go!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/patmorita/hermano-game-boy
